    "text": "put vFig. 16w.\nOften it can be separated into a Rn￿→Rsynapse function κz and a R￿→Rneuron activation\nfunctionαz so thatρ=α◦κ. The functions κandαcan have the following forms:\nκ:vy(￿)\n1,. . ,y(￿)\nn|w(￿)\n0j,. . ,w(￿)\nnjw→\n\n\n\nw(￿)\n0jy\nn￿\ni=1\ny(￿)\ni w(￿)\nij Sum,\nw(￿)\n0jy\nn￿\ni=1\n￿\ny(￿)\ni w(￿)\nij\n￿2\nSum of squares ,\nw(￿)\n0jy\nn￿\ni=1\n|y(￿)\ni w(￿)\nij| Sum of absolutes ,\nv71w\nα:x→\n\n\n\nx Linear,\n1\n1ye−kx Sigmoid,\nex−e−x\nexye−x Tanh,\ne−x2/2 Radial.\nv72w",
    "metadata": {
