    "text": "h\nevento The weight updates are obtained from Eqso h xwi and h xxi by removing the event summationso\nIn this case it is important to use a well randomised training sampleo Online learning is the learning\nmethod implemented in TMV Ao\nBFGS\nThe BroydennFletchernGoldfarbnShannon hBFGSi method [ su]d i ﬀers from back propagation by the\nuse of second derivatives of the error function to adapt the synapse weight by an algorithm which\nis composed of four main stepso",
