    "text": "the error function to adapt the synapse weight by an algorithm which\nis composed of four main stepso\nro Two vectorsm D and Y are calculatedo The vector of weight changes D represents the evolution\nbetween one iteration of the algorithm h k−ri to the next h kio Each synapse weight corresponds\nto one element of the vectoro The vector Y is the vector of gradient errorso\nD\n(k)\ni = w\n(k)\ni −w\n(k−1)\ni , hxyi\nY\n(k)\ni = g\n(k)\ni −g\n(k−1)\ni , hx9i",
