    "text": "e vector of gradient errorso\nD\n(k)\ni = w\n(k)\ni −w\n(k−1)\ni , hxyi\nY\n(k)\ni = g\n(k)\ni −g\n(k−1)\ni , hx9i\nwhere iis the synapse indexm gi is the inth synapse gradientm 28\nwi is the weight of the inth\nsynapsem and kdenotes the iteration countero\nso Approximate the inverse of the Hessian matrixm H−1\nm at iteration kby\nH−1(k)\n=\nD·DT\n·hr l YT\n·H−1(k−1)\n·Yi\nYT ·D\n−D·YT\n·H l H ·Y ·DT\nl H−1(k−1)\n, hyqi\nwhere superscripts h ki are implicit for D and Yo\nto Estimate the vector of weight changes by\nD(k)",
