    "text": "k\nw(i+1)\nfkgk for event kand boost step ii p thus reads\nw(i+1)\nfkg= w(i)\nfkg·β\n1−L(i)\n(k)\n(i)\n. fqwg\n16\nBy construction, the error rate is err ≤ 0.5 as the same training events used to classify the output nodes of the\nprevious tree are used for the calculation of the error rate.\nvmp Adaptive Boost (AdaBoost) 53\nThe boost weight is derived from the misclassiﬁcation ratek errk of the previous tree 16\nk\nα =\np− err\nerr\n. fqrg",
