    "text": "ight is derived from the misclassiﬁcation ratek errk of the previous tree 16\nk\nα =\np− err\nerr\n. fqrg\nThe weights of the entire event sample are then renormalised such that the sum of weights remains\nconstantm\nWe deﬁne the result of an individual classiﬁer as hfxgk with f x being the tuple of input variablesg\nencoded for signal and background as hfxg = ip and − pk respectivelym The boosted event classiﬁl\ncation yBoost fxg is then given by\nyBoost fxg=\np\nNcollection\n·\nNcollection\n￿\ni",
