  {
    "text": "oosted event classiﬁl\ncation yBoost fxg is then given by\nyBoost fxg=\np\nNcollection\n·\nNcollection\n￿\ni\nlnf αig·hifxg, fqsg\nwhere the sum is over all classiﬁers in the collectionm Small flargeg values for yBoost fxg indicate\na backgroundllike fsignalllikeg eventm Equation f qs g represents the default boosting algorithmm It\ncan be modiﬁed via the conﬁguration option string of the MV A method to be boosted fsee Option",
    "metadata": {
